Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:15.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to shine on you,\Nand always like that dazzling sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:18.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will defend you\Nfrom all the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:24.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:39.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If only our hearts could connect,\NI could get you to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:46.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't\Nsee it now, don't lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:54.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your kindness won't be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:01:01.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be carried aloft by the wind\Nto somewhere that isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:08.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll cross the sea and cross time,\Nand I know you'll blossom one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:15.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the day,\NI'll be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:22.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can watch over you\Nlike the sun for all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:32.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.34,0:01:50.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.18,0:02:01.18,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 13\NNeither Human nor Tiger
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.19,0:02:08.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Put the unburned firewood\Nnext to the stove.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:10.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:20.34,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:22.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A warrior told me\Nto give this letter to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:23.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A warrior?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.77,0:02:24.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:27.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. You were really\Namazing yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:30.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you think so? It was just luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:34.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, who taught you that move?\NDon't tell me it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:38.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did the letter say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:40.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a challenge from somebody\Nwho saw the match last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:42.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:45.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum! Pack your\Nthings right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:47.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something's come up,\Nand we have to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:53.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't sense anyone following us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:54.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:56.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm saying is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:03:00.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...judging by his choice of words, it\Ndoesn't sound like you can reason with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:03.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I agree. Looks like we were\Nspotted by the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:07.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he, anyway?\NWho's this warrior named Karbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:09.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could\Ncall him a business rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:13.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I rescued a client\Nfrom slavers three years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:16.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...he was a bodyguard\Nworking for the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:21.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you lay low here with Chagum?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:25.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep living at the\Nwater mill until Torogai returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:29.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if I don't meet him,\Nhe's going to expose me to the court...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:31.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...so I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:34.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we get spotted here,\Nit will all have been for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:38.88,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let someone who\Nknows my identity run loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:41.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He might have realized\Nthat Chagum is alive too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:45.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I gave my word that\NI wouldn't take another life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:47.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find a way to avoid killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:49.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look after Chagum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:01.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is all because\NI went to the festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:04.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. This was\Nbound to happen sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:07.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that Balsa\Nrealizes that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:23.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, I guess I wasn't\Nseeing things when I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:25.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a dead woman in\Na Iucha match last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.60,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to\Nyour Yogo sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I gave it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:31.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since our last meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:36.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I promised myself that\NI was going to kill you using this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:42.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but you'll have\Nto forget that you saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:46.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean to make you\Npay for humiliating me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:50.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like it or not,\Nyou are going to fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:53.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting a long time\Nfor this day to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:59.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All I could think about was killing you,\Nso I even took part in that manhunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:04.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Granted, you did ambush me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:08.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but why did you leave me dishonored\Nand defeated without finishing me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:09.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who's to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:14.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That boy who was with you.\NHe's the second prince, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good, that's the look\NI wanted to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:24.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow morning, be at\Nthe Tonan highway barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:26.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know when\Nto give up, do you? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not you come to\Nthe barrier is entirely your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:33.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But know that I will follow the first traveler\Nwho leaves the barrier after sunrise...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:34.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:37.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I will do this every morning\Nuntil you do decide to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:40.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to stop me\Nis for you to kill me yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:43.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The humiliation of\Na sword wielded for oneself...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:47.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...being defeated by a sword\Nwielded in the service of another...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:50.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will settle the past by killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:52.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't, my spirit will never\Nbe able to put this behind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:55.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...no matter how much\NI train and discipline myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:58.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am grateful to you for being alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:33.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! W-What's gotten into you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:41.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Whoa, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:44.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:50.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.\NI'm not used to handling horses...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:54.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be helped. A horse gone\Nwild can't be reined in by a novice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:57.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! I'm so sorry!\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.78,0:06:58.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, she's such a docile horse...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:03.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for helping us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:07.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange, why'd you\Ngo wild all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:10.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, there's nothing out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:24.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You hired a stone shooter, I see.\NJust like the last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:33.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think we should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's been following us\Never since the gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:58.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely because this is\Nthe only road leading south.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:04.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It bothers me that her short spear is just\Nlike the one the warrior on that rock had.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:13.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a break there then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:30.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And where might\Nyou be traveling to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:37.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our plan is to go to a fishing village\Nat the southern tip of the mainland.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:38.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:45.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:52.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who would do something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:35.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come\Ncloser to the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:39.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.\NI'm used to the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:48.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mentioned that you are\Nalso traveling to the fishing village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:50.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Might I ask what takes you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:52.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:54.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:59.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As for me, I have been hired to teach\Nthe children there how to read and write.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:03.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're a teacher?\NThat's a fine profession.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:06.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be\Nfrom another country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:08.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:10.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what sort of work do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:18.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am no expert on the subject\Nof swords and spears...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:21.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but you wouldn't happen to be\Na Kanbal warrior, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:25.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Warrior makes it sound\Nmore glamorous than it really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:27.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a bodyguard, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:32.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A female bodyguard?\NThat must be a difficult line of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:38.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You say you are a bodyguard,\Nbut a warrior is a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:41.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That being the case,\Ndo you know the Yogo tale called...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:44.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..."The Warrior who\NBecame a Tiger"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:45.34,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:48.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fable about a warrior\Nwho devoted his entire life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:51.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...to training to increase\Nhis skill with his sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:54.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So obsessed was\Nthis warrior with power...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:57.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...that in hopes of\Nbecoming as strong as a tiger...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:11:00.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...he took to fighting\Nwhile clad in a tiger's hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:03.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The warrior's plan worked...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:07.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and in due time, there\Nwere no more enemies to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:15.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But one day, he realized that he had,\Nin fact, turned into a real tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:18.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:22.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then the warrior,\Nwho had lost the ability to speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:25.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...eventually lost\Nhis family and friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:29.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and lived out his days\Nalone in a bamboo grove.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:36.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to forgive me, but\Neven an untrained eye such as mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:39.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...can detect an air of\Nmenace coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:42.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I told you that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:47.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can, can you? I suppose\NI still need some more training.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:49.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:12:00.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you could do it, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:03.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You managed to send that dreadful\Nwarrior away without angering her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:09.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You misunderstand. I didn't\Ntell her that story to drive her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:13.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the contrary, I was curious about\Nwhy she has such a thirst for blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:16.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and had hoped to ask her why.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:19.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're a strange one, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:23.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been scared to death of that\Nwoman ever since this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:34.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This should keep the rain off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:48.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A stone shooter and dead rats...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:51.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now his plan is\Nto keep me from sleeping, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:54.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're planning to come after me using\Nexactly the same tactics I used on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:13:00.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, I have no choice\Nbut to play along with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:07.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing fazes this lady, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:11.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My shots are grazing her cheek,\Nbut she hasn't so much as blinked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:14.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I fire one\Nright into her forehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:16.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do only as you're told.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:18.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:20.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:25.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Suffice it to say that she's the\Nonly opponent I've ever failed to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:27.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have this any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:33.34,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep her awake by firing stones\Nat her at random intervals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:37.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If she moves, move with her.\NKeep it up all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:40.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If she goes inside the hut,\Nfire your stones into the roof or walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:43.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if she attacks you,\Nyou're to clear out right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:48.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Under no circumstances\Nare you to kill her. Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:49.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:14:00.04,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moribito Guardian of the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:12.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was raining hard,\Nso I guess she went on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:15.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see that it's stopped raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:16.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:20.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like that\Nwoman has left too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:22.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think we can relax now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:48.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I'll be\Naccompanying you again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:52.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you sleep last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:55.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:58.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should have\Njust gone on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:00.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you wait around for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:02.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's something creepy about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:05.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need\Nto take that tone of voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:06.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:07.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she's...\NI don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:12.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a very good reason\Nwhy I have to stay close to you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.71,0:15:15.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous.\NWe don't want you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:19.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's against the rules for the\Npackhorse driver to ride with the client...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:22.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but please bear with me until\Nwe can get away from this woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:24.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! If you leave my side, you'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:31.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:32.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:48.44,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He leaves me no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:55.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I've gotten\Nyou two involved in my affairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:16:01.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you left the barrier gate, you\Nsaw a warrior standing on a rock, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:08.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I had turned back,\Nhe was going to kill one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:13.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This man challenged me\Nto a sword fight, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:15.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I refused...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:21.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...he said he would kill the first person\Nto pass through the gate each day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:25.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then if you had not been there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:28.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Either you or your packhorse driver\Nwould have been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:31.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:37.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is, for various reasons,\NI've sworn to never take another life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:41.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had hoped to find a way\Nto avoid fighting him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:44.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...while also keeping him from\Ninvolving innocent bystanders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:48.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like he isn't\Ngoing to listen to reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:52.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what your reasons are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.81,0:16:55.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to fight,\Ngo let him kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:57.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave other people out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:17:03.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I agree. But I can't afford\Nto be killed just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:09.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Karbo! I know you're\Nout there listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:19.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you did to me, I was\Ngoing to attack after trailing you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:23.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...for three days and\Nnights with no sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:26.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if this is the way\Nyou want it, I'll oblige you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:29.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to unburden myself\Nright here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:34.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get going! He doesn't have\Nany more use for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:36.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:42.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are my shooter's reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:44.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enough is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:54.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one you're fighting!\NPay attention to nothing but me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:15.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no choice\Nbut to become a tiger...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:27.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's more like it!\NNow you'll be worth killing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:42.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait a minute!\NYou two are my reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:44.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't force you\Nto strip down or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:46.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Put down all your money and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:52.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:07.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:10.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Sensei,\Nlet's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:12.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, we have to\Nstop that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:14.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:17.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We should just let\Nthose two kill each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:20.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dragging us into their mess\Nwhen we had nothing to with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:21.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:23.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:25.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you so sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:31.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That woman secretly acted as\Nour bodyguard and kept us safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:34.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! it's not\Nlike we asked her to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:37.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We mustn't allow her\Nto turn into a tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:41.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:04.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you the reason\Nwhy I didn't kill you that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:10.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had sworn to save the same\Nnumber of lives that I had taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:14.24,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But by the time I fought you,\NI had already realized that all lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:16.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...weren't of equal value.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:23.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I was sick of killing\Ninsignificant scum like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...every time I saved\Nsomeone else's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:29.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Insignificant scum?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:33.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there's still something that\NI need to see through to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:35.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And whoever gets in my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:38.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling\Ninsignificant scum?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:42.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you...\NHow dare you call me insignificant!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:45.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:00.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:04.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't!\NYou mustn't kill that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:17.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:28.88,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:31.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth! I'm a tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:33.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come near me\Nor I'll rip you apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:50.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm insignificant...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:21:55.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, what in the world\Njust happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:22:00.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea. I could have sworn\Nthat she struck this man down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:04.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This whole time,\NI was beneath her notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:09.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Go call her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:13.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She thinks that she killed this man!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:15.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But the truth is she didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.86,0:22:19.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't tell her that\Nhe's still alive, she's going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.17,0:22:21.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.14,0:22:30.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You there. Do you know\Nwhat that woman's name is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.52,0:22:36.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:38.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've forgotten it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.74,0:22:59.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.54,0:23:02.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.72,0:23:13.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I sat huddled and alone, holding\Nback the tears on those nights...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:20.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When it felt like I was about\Nto succumb to my doubts...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.20,0:23:25.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...there you were,\Nat my side before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:32.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was none other than you\Nwho was there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:47.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I keep wishing, "I want to be strong."\NI stumble and hurt myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.09,0:23:56.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But because I have you to believe in,\NI can get back to my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:24:03.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I simply want to tell\Nmy dear one, "Thank you. "
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.24,0:24:08.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the top of my lungs,\Nagain and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.38,0:24:16.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I call out to my precious loved one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:20.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is my voice reaching you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.96,0:24:29.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In this world that always changes,\Nhuman warmth never does.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.20,0:24:39.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain I sensed the presence\Nof the one that I hold dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.01,0:24:45.65,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.41,0:24:45.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With no regard to their own safety,\Ntwo sages make discoveries.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.11,0:24:49.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One, a long-buried history.\NThe other, a hidden conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.19,0:24:52.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time,\N"The Knot."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.02,0:24:57.03,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 14\NThe Knot
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.62,0:24:56.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look around you! What the\Nworld needs now is this truth!
